    <section id="aboutUs">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="heading text-center">
                <h2>About Us</h2>
                <p>
                    Usal Clinic is a community-based healthcare center serving the students and staff of USAL University. Our
                    mission is to foster a healthy campus environment through accessible, high-quality, and compassionate care.
                </p>

            </div>
            <div class="row feature design">
                <div class="six columns right">
                    <h3>Now Located at the USAL Campus</h3>
                    <p>
                        We are excited to announce that Usal Clinic is now officially located within the USAL university campus.
                        This strategic move allows us to be closer to the community we serve—students, faculty, and staff—making
                        access to healthcare more convenient and integrated into daily university life. Our clinic maintains a clean
                        and modern design, ensuring a welcoming and professional environment for everyone who walks through our
                        doors. We believe that being on campus not only enhances accessibility but also strengthens our mission to
                        promote wellness and support the academic journey through quality care.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        As we continue to grow, we’re already planning for the future. Our vision includes building a dedicated
                        clinic facility right next to the university. This small but fully equipped medical building will allow us
                        to expand our services, introduce new specialties, and provide a more comprehensive healthcare experience to
                        our patients.
                    </p>

